description: Eine Kreatur aus den Tiefen des Meeres gibt Rätsel auf. Augenscheinlich trägt das Wesen mit den Tentakeln einen Anzug, muss also, zieht man die Beschaffenheit der Bekleidung heran, intelligent sein. Die Obduktion findet leider nicht unter Ausschluss anderer Organismen statt. Eine Ratte hat sich in den Raum geschlichen.
name: Das Grab des Priesters Frollo

description: Das Undenkbare ist geschehen. Die Südstaaten haben ihre Unabhängigkeit erlangt. Der Präsident der Union, Abraham Lincoln, war gezwungen, einen Friedensvertrag mit Jefferson Davais, dem Präsidenten der Konföderation, zu unterschreiben.
name: Jack Tupper

description: 1865. Kap von La Hague. In einem neuen Kohlekraftwerk produziert Frankreich Energie, um mit den neuartigen Glühbirnen den Westen des Landes künftig beleuchten zu können. Die Zukunft ist in der Gegenwart angekommen.
name: La Hague

description: Alamo! Ein Fort in Texas wird am 6. März 1836 zur traurigen Legende. Ein fürchterlich geringe Anzahl texanischer Verteidiger unterliegt im dritten Ansturm der Armee des mexikanischen Generals Santa Anna. Als sich das Gemetzel seinem Ende nähert, erfüllt Davy Crockett eine letzte, vielleicht die wichtigste Aufgabe dieses Tages.
name: Jacob's Well

description:
Tales for the bold. Ideas for the strange. Ulises Farinas, Erick Freitas, and a cavalcade of new talents bring to life amazing fantastical tales: Founding father Ben Franklin fighting legendary dragons! A man discovers his dog's secret life! A boy finds the ultimate wish fulfillment! And a tale of a long-lost friend coming back...for revenge!

Contents

  • Ben Franklin, Dragon Hunter
  • Giant Laser Rifle
  • Fishbone
  • 1935

description: Kevin Nivek, head of the Secret Service and in charge of security for the President of the United States, is fired after an assassination attempt almost succeeds. While investigating what he believes is a conspiracy among the various American intelligence services, he meets Debrah, a mysterious and formidable young woman who works for a secret organization. He learns that for centuries, and from deep in the shadows, the Stryx have influenced human destiny.
name: Shadows

description: Kevin Nivek, head of the Secret Service and in charge of security for the President of the United States, is fired after an assassination attempt almost succeeds. While investigating what he believes is a conspiracy among the various American intelligence services, he meets Debrah, a mysterious and formidable young woman who works for a secret organization. He learns that for centuries, and from deep in the shadows, the Stryx have influenced human destiny.
name: Traps

description: Crombie, Secretary of State for Defense, commits suicide under the influence of a Stryx. Having learned the truth about his death, Nivek is now being closely followed by the secret services. At the same time, Debrah discovers that winged creatures were involved in the murder of Grosvenor...
name: The Grip

description:
Desert of Utah. Commissioned to destroy a consignment of weapons, the Shadow discovers that the convoy transports something quite different.

Meanwhile, Nolan progresses in the uncovering the affairs of Grosvenor and Crombie; according to his old friend Joshua, undoubtedly the Stryx are responsible.
name: Experiments

description:
The crew of a Boulton Paul Defiant night-fighter were puzzled. Why was an Airspeed Oxford trainer aircraft flying above England under cover of darkness? The gunner wondered if perhaps something secretive was going on.

How right he was. But there was no way that he could have known that the Oxford was being flown by a German crew, and was an integral part of an audacious plan by the Nazis to snatch back one of their spies.

At times the Home Front was almost as dangerous as the Front Line.
name: Home Front Heroes

description:
Ted Malloy knew him as Corporal Don Granger of the Australian Army, his best pal, young, dark-haired and full of spirit.

The Kachins, a Burmese tribe, knew him as "Urgu" - their Holy Man, chief and river god, tall with a lined face, bronzed skin, a mop of snow-white hair, and no memory of any past.

Ted and Don were the only two men ever to escape from "Death Valley", the dreaded Japanese labour camp, where men died by inches under the blazing sun and the whips of the guards.

The tale of how Ted got clear and how Don became Urgu truly is a thrilling one.

Note: Originally published as Commando No 198 (January 1966).
name: The Great Escape

description:
Brothers Vic and George Adams were part of a Pacific Expeditionary Force mortar team. They had been tasked with engaging the Japanese on Mono Island in the South Pacific.

Their superior officer, Lieutenant Jeff Danten, was not keen on mortars, seeing them as a waste of time compared to a decent machine-gun. It didn't help that Danten was also impatient and reckless, too eager to get into battle without decent tactics.

It looked like the Mortar Boys had more than just the enemy to worry about…
name: The Mortar Boys

description:
When Fred Burke made a vow to his dead mate that he would fight to the last to see the war won, it wouldn't be his fault if the Allies lost, for Fred was a man of his word. So in Fred's book anything went - like breaking out of a prison camp for a start, then after commandeering a civilian vehicle, battling alongside the partisans to hold a vital bridge. Fred just went on fighting and fighting…

Note: Originally published as Commando No 1108 (March 1977) and was re-issued as No 2443 (February 1991).
name: Fight To the Last

description: The hardest thing for Batman is to admit his greatest strength: He's just one man, and sometimes he needs help. With so much at stake, will he turn to help of the Super variety? This oversized paper-over-boards COLLECTOR'S EDITION features both stories from DARK KNIGHT III: THE MASTER RACE #3 at the same size!
name: Book Three

volume.name: Dark Knight III: The Master Race Collector's Edition

description: The siege of London continues. Mera is locked in a life and death struggle with the Kraken. And just when hope is on the horizon, a newer and deadlier threat emerges.
name: The Battle of Britain Part 4 of 6

description:
As a team of expendable but highly trained mercenaries makes its way through the city, threats they never could have imagined hit them at every turn. How can one survive inside of a city run by evil?

Bigby has all the pieces to solve the case, but Bloody Mary—or rather, a lot of Bloody Marys—will use those pieces to carve him to ribbons. And in the backup tales, our villains have a conversation with a dead king, and strike the bargain that changes everything.

The Galaxy Sisters haven't spoken in five years. Mallori Galaxy and the rest of her team have just successfully completed the sale of Illegal Psychotropic substances. Tanna Galaxy has accompanied a team of Intergalactic Union soldiers on their mission to

In a world, where on that fateful day in New York, the Ghostbusters did NOT cross streams, and were thus unable to destroy Gozer or close his portal. Now, 31 days later, NYC has descended into chaos and ruin, ruled with the deliciously soft fist of... THE STAY-PUFT MARSHMALLOW MAN!

1864, under an imaginary Second Empire, Napoléon III uses his army and his secret service to study certain phenomena relating to the occult and to popular legends. His goal is quite simple: achieving world supremacy.

In Guernesey, in the depths of Hauteville House, Victor Hugo's home in exile, a small group of Republican special agents attempt to thwart the Imperial projects. For his first mission, Agent Gavroche is sent to Mexico to help the Resistance to organize against Maximilian's troops. Maximilian, a puppet Emperor set in place by Napoléon III, is doing some rather strange research in the Maya temples for his master...
name: Zelda

description:
1864, under an imaginary Second Empire, Napoléon III uses his army and his secret service to study certain phenomena relating to the occult and to popular legends. His goal is quite simple: achieving world supremacy.

On May 15th, 1864, the special forces of Emperor Napoleon III intervene on the Mexican soil in pursuit of the Republican agent Gavroche. Fearing for his safety, the headquarters of the French Resistance send Églantine on her first mission in the field.

She finds herself under the scrutiny of the fearless Zelda, who's still in the service of American counter-intelligence.
name: Destination Tulum

description: Eglantine, the Republicans' new recruit, has infiltrated the party of Ernest de la Touque, a diplomat of Napoleon III. Landing in Charleston, ravaged by the American Civil War, she has to discover what the Emperor wants to negotiate with the Confederate states.
name: The Ghost Steamer

description:
Atlanta, 1864. Eglantine has discovered what Emperor Napoleon III plans to negotiate with the Confederate States of the South: the use of a monstrous and mystical, living weapon discovered in the ruins of a Mayan temple. Meanwhile, Zelda, Gavroche, and Georges, taken prisoner by the Confederates, are transferred by train towards Atlanta where General Hood wants to question them before initiating the final battle...

The grand finale of a spectacular adventure!
name: Atlanta

description: A young Buddhist monk must defeat luchador demons and resist the thrall of an enchanted dagger in order to reclaim her own destiny and end a cycle of violence that stretches across lifetimes!
As the Duke’s legion of undead warriors attacks, Diana must decide whether to chase her answers of home, or use her new strengths to defend the Outsiders.
name: Chapter Eighteen

description: The GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY are in tiny/big trouble! Gamora, Rocket, and Groot are stuck in a crumbling mini dimension, and Drax is possessed by the little alien who trapped them! It's up to Peter Quill to save…everyone!

volume.name: Marvel Universe Guardians of the Galaxy Infinite Comic

description: As Mercy's mom, Faustia, gains control of the access point between Heaven, Earth and Hell, Mercy must team with an unlikely crew of allies to stop the evil demoness' micro-Armageddon from going worldwide.

The untold first meeting of Twilight and baby Spike! Twilight is given her most difficult task yet by Princess Celestia when she is told to take care of a baby dragon who is quite a handful! Will Twilight learn the right lesson in caring for another?

description: This means WAR! Archie and long-time rival Reggie have been on good terms lately, but that's about to change! The constant double-crosses and sabotages have taken their toll, and the two teens are ready for the ultimate prank battle! Can Archie withstand Reggie's dirty tricks? Will Reggie ruin Archie's reputation once and for all? Will their "friendship" ever be the same?
name: Archie VS Reggie

description: In Volume 1 of Ruined, Andrew and Catherine become acquainted with each other, but they may have to move more slowly than anticipated...
name: Volume 1

description:
No longer the hunted, Calie and Violet become the hunters as they travel to New Orleans in search of the infestations of Wonderland. There, they uncover a string of disappearances connected to one of their old enemies, the March Hare. But what does this denizen of Wonderland want with the men and women he's collecting?

description: Revisit a blue-and-golden age for the X-Men in Battleworld's most animated realm! The '90s-era team is as uncanny as ever: Professor X, Cyclops, Storm, Wolverine, Rogue, Gambit and - yes! - Jubilee. And when the Clear Mountain Project purports to offer evil mutants a chance at rehabilitation, it's up to the X-Men to investigate! As things go wrong, they'll face some of their decade's fiercest foes, like Cyber and Omega Red - but who on Battleworld is the Shadow Queen?! With the X-Men in deep trouble, will anyone step up to save the domain of Westchester from a future of fear and hatred? How about an X-Force '92 lineup featuring Cable, Deadpool, Domino, Psylocke, Archangel and Bishop? Could this totally tubular tale be any more '90s? Collecting X-MEN '92 (2015) #1-4.
name: Volume 0

description: When business is down in March, Scott Lang's Ant-Man Security Solutions will take just about any job offered to them- including stealing back stolen goods! But all is not as it seems! Join writer Amy Chu and artist Ryan Browne as they team together for this Spring Break themed heist!

volume.name: A Year of Marvels: March Infinite Comic

description: Blonde and bubbly, not to mention bumbling, Suzie is a gorgeous girl with a clumsy streak that could rival Archie's! She's got a good heart and likes to help -- though sometimes that's worse than having no help at all! When she's not hopping from job to job, she's hopping from boyfriend to boyfriend. Will she go steady with the handsome Greg or the lovable lunkhead Ferdie? Find out in over 50 pages of laughs!
name: Suzie Comics

description: "Monika" ist ein Thriller voller Erotik, Kunst, Kybernetik und Terrorismus. Monika, das ist gleichzeitig der Name zweier Schwestern, die unterschiedlicher nicht sein könnten. Die eine lässt sich durch das Leben treiben, nie wissend, wohin es sie verschlägt. Ihr Leben verbringt sie mit Fremden, ihr wahres Ich aber offenbart sie nur einem Roboter, der sie fasziniert. Die andere Monika scheint alles zu wissen, alles zu kontrollieren und ist in terroristische Machenschaften verstrickt. Projekt Monika bringt die beiden unterschiedlichen Schwestern wieder zusammen, lässt sie sich gegenübertreten und zeigt ihnen, wer sie wirklich sind und dass das nicht zwangsweise dem entspricht, was sie voneinander erwartet hatten ...
name: Ball der Masken
